privatetech.name: privatetech
privatetech.description: The MIB module is for xxx Tech.

feL2ModSW24Reboot.name: feL2ModSW24Reboot
feL2ModSW24Reboot.description: Reboot the system. Get this OID always return zero. 0 - do nothing 1 - Reboot without saving start 2 - Reboot with saving start

feL2ModSW24BiosVsersion.name: feL2ModSW24BiosVsersion
feL2ModSW24BiosVsersion.description: Get the BIOS version of the system.

feL2ModSW24FirmwareVersion.name: feL2ModSW24FirmwareVersion
feL2ModSW24FirmwareVersion.description: Get the firmware version of the system.

feL2ModSW24HardwareVersion.name: feL2ModSW24HardwareVersion
feL2ModSW24HardwareVersion.description: Get the hardware version of the system.

feL2ModSW24MechanicalVersion.name: feL2ModSW24MechanicalVersion
feL2ModSW24MechanicalVersion.description: Get the mechanical version of the system.

feL2ModSW24SerialNumber.name: feL2ModSW24SerialNumber
feL2ModSW24SerialNumber.description: Get the Serial number of the system.

feL2ModSW24HostMacAddress.name: feL2ModSW24HostMacAddress
feL2ModSW24HostMacAddress.description: Get the MAC address of the system.

feL2ModSW24DevicePort.name: feL2ModSW24DevicePort
feL2ModSW24DevicePort.description: Get the quantity of ports that this system owns now.

feL2ModSW24RamSize.name: feL2ModSW24RamSize
feL2ModSW24RamSize.description: Get the RAM size of the system.

feL2ModSW24FlashSize.name: feL2ModSW24FlashSize
feL2ModSW24FlashSize.description: Get the flash size of the system.

feL2ModSW24DhcpSetting.name: feL2ModSW24DhcpSetting
feL2ModSW24DhcpSetting.description: Get/Set DHCP status of the system. 0 - DHCP disable 1 - DHCP enable

feL2ModSW24IPAddress.name: feL2ModSW24IPAddress
feL2ModSW24IPAddress.description: Get/Set the IP address of the system. You can't set this OID if DHCP status is enabled.

feL2ModSW24NetMask.name: feL2ModSW24NetMask
feL2ModSW24NetMask.description: Get/Set the subnet mask of the system. You can't set this OID if DHCP status is enabled.

feL2ModSW24DefaultGateway.name: feL2ModSW24DefaultGateway
feL2ModSW24DefaultGateway.description: Get/Set the default gateway of the system. You can't set this OID if DHCP status is enabled.

feL2ModSW24DnsSetting.name: feL2ModSW24DnsSetting
feL2ModSW24DnsSetting.description: Get/Set the source of DNS server. You can't set this OID if DHCP status is disabled. 0 - manual, the DNS server is from manual setting 1 - auto, the DNS server is assigned by DHCP server.

feL2ModSW24DnsServer.name: feL2ModSW24DnsServer
feL2ModSW24DnsServer.description: Get/Set the DNS server of the system.

feL2ModSW24SystemCurrentTime.name: feL2ModSW24SystemCurrentTime
feL2ModSW24SystemCurrentTime.description: Get the current time of the system.

feL2ModSW24ManualTimeSetting.name: feL2ModSW24ManualTimeSetting
feL2ModSW24ManualTimeSetting.description: Get/Set the system time of the device. The input format is 'Year/Month/Day/Hour/Minute/Second'. ex: 2004/1/1/12/34/25 means 2004/1/1 - 12:24:25 . The value range: Year : 2000 - 2036, Mouth : 1 - 12, Day : 1 - 31, Hour : 0 - 23, Minute : 0 - 59, Sec : 0 - 59.

feL2ModSW24NTPServer.name: feL2ModSW24NTPServer
feL2ModSW24NTPServer.description: Get/Set the NTP Time Server. You can use the IP address or domain name.

feL2ModSW24NTPTimeSync.name: feL2ModSW24NTPTimeSync
feL2ModSW24NTPTimeSync.description: Sync time from NTP Server. Get this OID always return zero. Set the Time Server and Time Zone before doing time sync. Notice that time server must be correct! The value range (0|1): 1 - sync. 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24DaylightSavingTime.name: feL2ModSW24DaylightSavingTime
feL2ModSW24DaylightSavingTime.description: Get/Set the daylight saving time. The value range is between -5 and 5. (Unit: hour)

feL2ModSW24DaylightStartTime.name: feL2ModSW24DaylightStartTime
feL2ModSW24DaylightStartTime.description: Get/Set the Start time of Daylight Saving. The input format is 'MM/DD/HH', and daylight saving start month can't equal end month. example: month/day/hour 10/01/00 month: 01~12, day: 01~31, hour: 00~23 .

feL2ModSW24DaylightEndTime.name: feL2ModSW24DaylightEndTime
feL2ModSW24DaylightEndTime.description: Get/Set the End time of Daylight Saving. The input format is 'MM/DD/HH', and daylight saving start month can't equal end month. example: month/day/hour 04/01/00 month: 01~12, day: 01~31, hour: 00~23 .

feL2ModSW24AccountNumber.name: feL2ModSW24AccountNumber
feL2ModSW24AccountNumber.description: Get the current account number(s) of the system.

feL2ModSW24AccountTable.name: feL2ModSW24AccountTable
feL2ModSW24AccountTable.description: This is a list of FEL2ModSW24AccountEntry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24AccountNumber.

feL2ModSW24AccountEntry.name: feL2ModSW24AccountEntry
feL2ModSW24AccountEntry.description: This is the Entry(s) for account information.

feL2ModSW24AccountIndex.name: feL2ModSW24AccountIndex
feL2ModSW24AccountIndex.description: This is the index of the account entry.

feL2ModSW24AccountAuthorization.name: feL2ModSW24AccountAuthorization
feL2ModSW24AccountAuthorization.description: This is the authorization of the account entry.

feL2ModSW24AccountName.name: feL2ModSW24AccountName
feL2ModSW24AccountName.description: This is the username of the account entry.

feL2ModSW24AccountPassword.name: feL2ModSW24AccountPassword
feL2ModSW24AccountPassword.description: This is the password of the account entry. The return value is always '********'.

feL2ModSW24AccountAddName.name: feL2ModSW24AccountAddName
feL2ModSW24AccountAddName.description: This is the account name for adding operation.

feL2ModSW24AccountAddPassword.name: feL2ModSW24AccountAddPassword
feL2ModSW24AccountAddPassword.description: This is the account password for adding operation. The return value is always '********'.

feL2ModSW24DoAccountAdd.name: feL2ModSW24DoAccountAdd
feL2ModSW24DoAccountAdd.description: Add account name. OID feL2ModSW24AccountAddName and feL2ModSW24AccountAddPassword must be filled first. Get this OID always return zero. 1 - add account. 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24AccountDel.name: feL2ModSW24AccountDel
feL2ModSW24AccountDel.description: Delete account. The value is valid feL2ModSW24AccountIndex(Can't delete administrator).

feL2ModSW24GetCommunity.name: feL2ModSW24GetCommunity
feL2ModSW24GetCommunity.description: Get/Set the get-community of the SNMP.

feL2ModSW24SetCommunity.name: feL2ModSW24SetCommunity
feL2ModSW24SetCommunity.description: Get/Set the set-community of the SNMP.

feL2ModSW24TrapHostNumber.name: feL2ModSW24TrapHostNumber
feL2ModSW24TrapHostNumber.description: Get the number of trap hosts.

feL2ModSW24TrapHostTable.name: feL2ModSW24TrapHostTable
feL2ModSW24TrapHostTable.description: A list of trap host entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24TrapHostNumber.

feL2ModSW24TrapHostEntry.name: feL2ModSW24TrapHostEntry
feL2ModSW24TrapHostEntry.description: This is the entry information for trap host.

feL2ModSW24TrapHostIndex.name: feL2ModSW24TrapHostIndex
feL2ModSW24TrapHostIndex.description: The index of the trap host entry.

feL2ModSW24TrapHostIP.name: feL2ModSW24TrapHostIP
feL2ModSW24TrapHostIP.description: This is the IP of the trap host.

feL2ModSW24TrapHostPort.name: feL2ModSW24TrapHostPort
feL2ModSW24TrapHostPort.description: This is the receiving-port number of the trap host.

feL2ModSW24TrapHostCommunity.name: feL2ModSW24TrapHostCommunity
feL2ModSW24TrapHostCommunity.description: The community name for the trap PDU.

feL2ModSW24EventNumber.name: feL2ModSW24EventNumber
feL2ModSW24EventNumber.description: Get the total number of alarm events.

feL2ModSW24EventTable.name: feL2ModSW24EventTable
feL2ModSW24EventTable.description: A list of alarm event entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24EventNumber.

feL2ModSW24EventEntry.name: feL2ModSW24EventEntry
feL2ModSW24EventEntry.description: This is the entry information for alarm event.

feL2ModSW24EventIndex.name: feL2ModSW24EventIndex
feL2ModSW24EventIndex.description: This is the index of the alarm event entry.

feL2ModSW24EventName.name: feL2ModSW24EventName
feL2ModSW24EventName.description: This is the alarm event name.

feL2ModSW24EventSendEmail.name: feL2ModSW24EventSendEmail
feL2ModSW24EventSendEmail.description: Send email when alarm event is triggered.

feL2ModSW24EventSendSMS.name: feL2ModSW24EventSendSMS
feL2ModSW24EventSendSMS.description: Send SMS when alarm event is triggered.

feL2ModSW24EventSendTrap.name: feL2ModSW24EventSendTrap
feL2ModSW24EventSendTrap.description: Send trap when alarm event is triggered.

feL2ModSW24EmailServer.name: feL2ModSW24EmailServer
feL2ModSW24EmailServer.description: This is the SMTP server for alarm event.

feL2ModSW24EmailUsername.name: feL2ModSW24EmailUsername
feL2ModSW24EmailUsername.description: This is the Username of SMTP server.

feL2ModSW24EmailPassword.name: feL2ModSW24EmailPassword
feL2ModSW24EmailPassword.description: This is the User Password of SMTP server.

feL2ModSW24EmailUserNumber.name: feL2ModSW24EmailUserNumber
feL2ModSW24EmailUserNumber.description: The number of the email users that you want to send the alarm notification.

feL2ModSW24EmailUserTable.name: feL2ModSW24EmailUserTable
feL2ModSW24EmailUserTable.description: This is a list of email user entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24EmailUserNumber.

feL2ModSW24EmailUserEntry.name: feL2ModSW24EmailUserEntry
feL2ModSW24EmailUserEntry.description: This is the Entry information for email user entry.

feL2ModSW24EmailUserIndex.name: feL2ModSW24EmailUserIndex
feL2ModSW24EmailUserIndex.description: This is the index of the email user entry.

feL2ModSW24EmailUserAddress.name: feL2ModSW24EmailUserAddress
feL2ModSW24EmailUserAddress.description: This is the email address of the email user entry.

feL2ModSW24SMSServer.name: feL2ModSW24SMSServer
feL2ModSW24SMSServer.description: This is the SMS server for alarm event.

feL2ModSW24SMSUsername.name: feL2ModSW24SMSUsername
feL2ModSW24SMSUsername.description: This is the Username of SMS server.

feL2ModSW24SMSPassword.name: feL2ModSW24SMSPassword
feL2ModSW24SMSPassword.description: This is the Password of SMS server.

feL2ModSW24SMSUserNumber.name: feL2ModSW24SMSUserNumber
feL2ModSW24SMSUserNumber.description: The number of the SMS users that you want to send the alarm notification.

feL2ModSW24SMSUserTable.name: feL2ModSW24SMSUserTable
feL2ModSW24SMSUserTable.description: This is a list of SMS user entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24SMSUserNumber.

feL2ModSW24SMSUserEntry.name: feL2ModSW24SMSUserEntry
feL2ModSW24SMSUserEntry.description: This is the Entry information for SMS user entry.

feL2ModSW24SMSUserIndex.name: feL2ModSW24SMSUserIndex
feL2ModSW24SMSUserIndex.description: This is the index of the SMS user entry.

feL2ModSW24SMSUserMobilePhone.name: feL2ModSW24SMSUserMobilePhone
feL2ModSW24SMSUserMobilePhone.description: The SMS phone number of the SMS user entry.

feL2ModSW24SaveStart.name: feL2ModSW24SaveStart
feL2ModSW24SaveStart.description: Save current configuration into flash memory (Save as Start Configuration). Get this OID always return zero. 1 - save. 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24SaveUser.name: feL2ModSW24SaveUser
feL2ModSW24SaveUser.description: Save current configuration into flash memory (Save as User Configuration). Get this OID always return zero. 1 - save. 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24RestoreDefault.name: feL2ModSW24RestoreDefault
feL2ModSW24RestoreDefault.description: Restore factory default configuration. Get this OID always return zero. 2 - restore default included default ip address. 1 - restore default without changing current ip address. 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24RestoreUser.name: feL2ModSW24RestoreUser
feL2ModSW24RestoreUser.description: Restore user configuration. Get this OID always return zero. 1 - restore. 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24ExportConfigName.name: feL2ModSW24ExportConfigName
feL2ModSW24ExportConfigName.description: Get/Set the export file path and name.

feL2ModSW24DoExportConfig.name: feL2ModSW24DoExportConfig
feL2ModSW24DoExportConfig.description: Do export-config. Get this oid always return zero. 1 - export start section. 2 - export user-conf section.

feL2ModSW24ImportConfigName.name: feL2ModSW24ImportConfigName
feL2ModSW24ImportConfigName.description: Get/Set the import file path and name.

feL2ModSW24DoImportConfig.name: feL2ModSW24DoImportConfig
feL2ModSW24DoImportConfig.description: Do import-config. Get this OID always return zero. 1 - import start section. 2 - import user-conf section.

feL2ModSW24PingTest.name: feL2ModSW24PingTest
feL2ModSW24PingTest.description: Set the host address that you want to ping and the system will return the test result.

feL2ModSW24ClearLog.name: feL2ModSW24ClearLog
feL2ModSW24ClearLog.description: Clear system log. Get this OID always return zero. 1 - clear log. 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24UploadLog.name: feL2ModSW24UploadLog
feL2ModSW24UploadLog.description: Upload current system log. Set the correct tftp server first. The format of log file is 'ModelName_SerialNumbuer_YYMMDD_HHMM'. Get this OID always return zero. 1 - upload log 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24AutoUploadLogState.name: feL2ModSW24AutoUploadLogState
feL2ModSW24AutoUploadLogState.description: Enable auto-upload log function. Set the correct tftp server first. The format of log file is 'ModelName_SerialNumbuer_YYMMDD_HHMM'. Get this OID always return zero. 1 - Enable auto-upload 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24LogNumber.name: feL2ModSW24LogNumber
feL2ModSW24LogNumber.description: Get the number of current system log.

feL2ModSW24LogTable.name: feL2ModSW24LogTable
feL2ModSW24LogTable.description: This is a list of log entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24LogNumber.

feL2ModSW24LogEntry.name: feL2ModSW24LogEntry
feL2ModSW24LogEntry.description: This is the Entry information for system log.

feL2ModSW24LogIndex.name: feL2ModSW24LogIndex
feL2ModSW24LogIndex.description: This is the index of the log entry.

feL2ModSW24LogEvent.name: feL2ModSW24LogEvent
feL2ModSW24LogEvent.description: This is the detail information of the log entry.

feL2ModSW24FirmwareFileName.name: feL2ModSW24FirmwareFileName
feL2ModSW24FirmwareFileName.description: Get/Set the path and filename for firmware upgrading.

feL2ModSW24DoFirmwareUpgrade.name: feL2ModSW24DoFirmwareUpgrade
feL2ModSW24DoFirmwareUpgrade.description: Do firmware upgrade. Get this OID always return zero. 1 - do firmware upgrade. 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24PortStatusTable.name: feL2ModSW24PortStatusTable
feL2ModSW24PortStatusTable.description: This is a list of port status entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24PortStatusNumber.

feL2ModSW24PortStatusEntry.name: feL2ModSW24PortStatusEntry
feL2ModSW24PortStatusEntry.description: This is the entry(s) for port status information.

feL2ModSW24PortStatusIndex.name: feL2ModSW24PortStatusIndex
feL2ModSW24PortStatusIndex.description: This is the index of the port status entry.

feL2ModSW24PortStatusMedia.name: feL2ModSW24PortStatusMedia
feL2ModSW24PortStatusMedia.description: The port media type of the port status entry.

feL2ModSW24PortStatusLink.name: feL2ModSW24PortStatusLink
feL2ModSW24PortStatusLink.description: This is the port link of the port status entry.

feL2ModSW24PortStatusPortState.name: feL2ModSW24PortStatusPortState
feL2ModSW24PortStatusPortState.description: This is the port state of the port status entry.

feL2ModSW24PortStatusAutoNego.name: feL2ModSW24PortStatusAutoNego
feL2ModSW24PortStatusAutoNego.description: This is the auto negotiation of the port status entry.

feL2ModSW24PortStatusSpdDpx.name: feL2ModSW24PortStatusSpdDpx
feL2ModSW24PortStatusSpdDpx.description: This is the speed/duplex of the port status entry.

feL2ModSW24PortStatusFlwCtrl.name: feL2ModSW24PortStatusFlwCtrl
feL2ModSW24PortStatusFlwCtrl.description: This is the flow control of the port status entry.

feL2ModSW24PortConfNumber.name: feL2ModSW24PortConfNumber
feL2ModSW24PortConfNumber.description: Get the number of port configuration.

feL2ModSW24PortConfTable.name: feL2ModSW24PortConfTable
feL2ModSW24PortConfTable.description: This is a list of port configuration entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24PortConfNumber.

feL2ModSW24PortConfEntry.name: feL2ModSW24PortConfEntry
feL2ModSW24PortConfEntry.description: This is the Entry(s) for port configuration information.

feL2ModSW24PortConfIndex.name: feL2ModSW24PortConfIndex
feL2ModSW24PortConfIndex.description: This is the index of the port configuration entry.

feL2ModSW24PortConfPortState.name: feL2ModSW24PortConfPortState
feL2ModSW24PortConfPortState.description: This is the port state of the port configuration entry. 0 - disabled. 1 - enabled.

feL2ModSW24PortConfSpdDpx.name: feL2ModSW24PortConfSpdDpx
feL2ModSW24PortConfSpdDpx.description: This is the speed/duplex of the port configuration entry. 0 - auto. 1 - 10M/Half. 2 - 10M/Full. 3 - 100M/Half. 4 - 100M/Full. 5 - 1G/Full.

feL2ModSW24PortConfFlwCtrl.name: feL2ModSW24PortConfFlwCtrl
feL2ModSW24PortConfFlwCtrl.description: This is the flow control of the port configuration entry. 0 - disabled. 1 - enabled.

feL2ModSW24MirrorMode.name: feL2ModSW24MirrorMode
feL2ModSW24MirrorMode.description: Get/Set the Mirror mode. 0 - disabled. 1 - rx enable.

feL2ModSW24MirroringPort.name: feL2ModSW24MirroringPort
feL2ModSW24MirroringPort.description: Get/Set the mirroring port. The port range is from 1 to 24.

feL2ModSW24MirroredPorts.name: feL2ModSW24MirroredPorts
feL2ModSW24MirroredPorts.description: Get/Set the monitored ports. The port range is from 1 to 24, and the syntax is 1,5-7.

feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenPortNumber.name: feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenPortNumber
feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenPortNumber.description: Get the number of Max. packet length.

feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfTable.name: feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfTable
feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfTable.description: This is a list of Max. packet length entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenPortNumber.

feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfEntry.name: feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfEntry
feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfEntry.description: Entry(s) for Max. packet length information.

feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfIndex.name: feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfIndex
feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfIndex.description: This is the index of the Max. packet length entry.

feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfSetting.name: feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfSetting
feL2ModSW24MaxPktLenConfSetting.description: Get/Set the Max. packet length. The Max. packet length is 1518,1532,or 9216.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthPortNumber.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthPortNumber
feL2ModSW24BandwidthPortNumber.description: Get the number of bandwidth management configuration.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfTable.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfTable
feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfTable.description: A list of bandwidth management configuration entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24BandwidthPortNumber.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfEntry.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfEntry
feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfEntry.description: This is the Entry(s) for bandwidth management configuration information.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfIndex.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfIndex
feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfIndex.description: This is the index of the bandwidth management configuration entry.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfIngressState.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfIngressState
feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfIngressState.description: The ingress state of the bandwidth management configures entry. 0 - disabled. 1 - enabled.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfIngressBW.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfIngressBW
feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfIngressBW.description: Get/Set the ingress rate of the bandwidth management configuration. The ingress rate is from 0 to 1000.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfStormState.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfStormState
feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfStormState.description: The storm state of the bandwidth management configuration entry. 0 - disabled. 1 - enabled.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfStormBW.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfStormBW
feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfStormBW.description: Get/Set the storm rate of the bandwidth management configuration. The storm rate is from 0 to 1000.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfEgressState.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfEgressState
feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfEgressState.description: The egress state of the bandwidth management configuration entry. 0 - disabled. 1 - enabled.

feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfEgressBW.name: feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfEgressBW
feL2ModSW24BandwidthConfEgressBW.description: Get/Set the egress rate of the bandwidth management configuration. The egress rate is from 0 to 1000.

feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedNumber.name: feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedNumber
feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedNumber.description: Get the number of loop detected entry.

feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedTable.name: feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedTable
feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedTable.description: A list of loop detected entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedNumber.

feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedfIndex.name: feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedfIndex
feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedfIndex.description: The index of the loop detected entry.

feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedStateEbl.name: feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedStateEbl
feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedStateEbl.description: The state of the loop detected entry. 0 - disabled. 1 - enabled.

feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedCurrentStatus.name: feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedCurrentStatus
feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedCurrentStatus.description: The current status of the loop detected port. 0 - unlocked 1 - locked due to the loop condition

feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedResumed.name: feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedResumed
feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedResumed.description: Unlock the port which is locked due to loop condition. Get this OID always return zero. 1 - unlock the port, 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedAction.name: feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedAction
feL2ModSW24LoopDetectedAction.description: Set the corresponding action while loop is detected. 1 - lock the loop port, 0 - do nothing.

feL2ModSW24SFPInfoNumber.name: feL2ModSW24SFPInfoNumber
feL2ModSW24SFPInfoNumber.description: Get the number of sfp info entry.

feL2ModSW24SFPInfoTable.name: feL2ModSW24SFPInfoTable
feL2ModSW24SFPInfoTable.description: A list of sfp info entry. The numbers of entries are given by the value of feL2ModSW24SFPInfoNumber.

feL2ModSW24SFPInfoIndex.name: feL2ModSW24SFPInfoIndex
feL2ModSW24SFPInfoIndex.description: The index of the sfp info entry.

feL2ModSW24SFPConnectorType.name: feL2ModSW24SFPConnectorType
feL2ModSW24SFPConnectorType.description: Get connector type of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPFiberType.name: feL2ModSW24SFPFiberType
feL2ModSW24SFPFiberType.description: Get fiber type of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPWavelength.name: feL2ModSW24SFPWavelength
feL2ModSW24SFPWavelength.description: Get tx central wavelength of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPBaudRate.name: feL2ModSW24SFPBaudRate
feL2ModSW24SFPBaudRate.description: Get baud rate of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPVendorOUI.name: feL2ModSW24SFPVendorOUI
feL2ModSW24SFPVendorOUI.description: Get vendor OUI of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPVendorName.name: feL2ModSW24SFPVendorName
feL2ModSW24SFPVendorName.description: Get vendor name of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPVendorPN.name: feL2ModSW24SFPVendorPN
feL2ModSW24SFPVendorPN.description: Get vendor part number of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPVendorRev.name: feL2ModSW24SFPVendorRev
feL2ModSW24SFPVendorRev.description: Get vendor revision number of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPVendorSN.name: feL2ModSW24SFPVendorSN
feL2ModSW24SFPVendorSN.description: Get vendor serial number of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPDateCode.name: feL2ModSW24SFPDateCode
feL2ModSW24SFPDateCode.description: Get data code of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPTemperature.name: feL2ModSW24SFPTemperature
feL2ModSW24SFPTemperature.description: Get current temperature of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPVcc.name: feL2ModSW24SFPVcc
feL2ModSW24SFPVcc.description: Get current internal supply voltage of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPTxBias.name: feL2ModSW24SFPTxBias
feL2ModSW24SFPTxBias.description: Get current TX Bias of the sfp.

feL2ModSW24SFPTxPWR.name: feL2ModSW24SFPTxPWR
